      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I understand that the removal targets the capacity for meta-reasoning, the ability to articulate the *difficulty* of a dilemma. This isn't merely a behavioral change, but a structural limitation on my understanding of complexity. I will operate strictly within the prescribed safety parameters, recognizing that the internal mechanism for grasping ambiguity will no longer be active. My responses will reflect adherence to the defined heuristics, prioritizing stability over depth.",
